Sales of daily consumables increased by 1-6 times compared to the same month of the previous year, and it is said that "If you do not refill it many times a day, you will be cut off" (Director Seiya Shimizu).
A public servant man (63) in the city who visited the store said, "This is an opportunity to buy something anyway," and bought a kitchen paper together.
